HEADWORD: Compaginate
<hw>Com*pag"i*nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>compaginare</ets>, <ets>compaginatum</ets>.]</ety> <def>To unite or
hold together; <as>as, the side pieces <ex>compaginate</ex> the
frame</as>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>W. Montagu.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
